historyItem.sql: select w.* from safe_kiosk_workflow w where ( trim(:cp) is null or w.visitor_type_code in ( select m.visitor_type_code from safe_cp_workflow_mapping m where m.collection_point_code = :cp ) ) and nvl2(trim(:event_ind), w.event_ind, 'Y') = nvl2(trim(:event_ind), trim(:event_ind), 'Y') and safe_request_permissions_pak.check_permission_sql ( :Uidtoken, '(kioskworkflowmenu)(visitoractionmenu)(guestDashboard)', 'getKioskWorkflowData', 'GET' ) = 'Y' and ( REGEXP_LIKE(safe_get_setting_or_null('product_install_string'), '(EM)') or w.event_ind != 'Y' ) order by to_number(w.workflow_order)
